context.title: Summary (All Projects)
context.description: This Summary tab aggregates resource allocation and actual effort across 9 active projects included in this export.

metric_definitions.allocated_hours_total: Allocated Hours (Total) is the sum of allocation totals across all included projects (lifetime allocation for these projects, regardless of reporting period).
metric_definitions.actual_hours_period: Actual Hours (Period) is the sum of actual hours recorded within the reporting period (2025-03-16 → 2026-01-31) across all included projects.
metric_definitions.effort_utilized_pct: Effort Utilized % = Actual Hours (Period) ÷ Allocated Hours (Total) × 100.

notes: If Allocated Hours exceeds actuals, it may indicate allocations extend beyond the selected reporting window.
